metadata.name: Mother's Blood
metadata.description:
If I had to describe the sea in one word it would be “respect”.

Not because of its immense power or vast knowledge.

But the wisdom it carries in every wavy heartbeat.

It still baffles me how we managed to ride through it.

As if mother let us bathe in the blood that continues to bring life to the world.

Sometimes it is a kind ride, and then she shows how her gentleness a choice.
